The HDMI20-OPTC-TX220-Pro is a HDMI 2.0 compatible extender pair for video, RS-232, and Gigabit Ethernet signals. It supports uncompressed 4K UHD resolution at 60Hz 4:4:4 and can extend signals up to 700 meters using OM3/OM4 fiber. Some highlighted features include Single Fiber Technology, advanced EDID Management, device control via Ethernet (TCP/IP), RS-232, and USB, as well as a built-in universal power supply. The extender is HDCP 2.2 compliant and recommended for rental and staging applications, 4K live events, and operation centers requiring future-proof solutions. 
For more detailed information, please visit the following link: [HDMI20-OPTC-TX220-Pro](https://lightware.com/products/extenders/hdmi20-optc-tx220-pro)

